preference.name: PSECopyAbsOccDuringVICreation
preference.preference_description: Controls copy of Absolute occurrence data from generic assembly to variant item on creation of a variant item. Valid Values: * false: Absolute Occurrence data is not copied on variant item creation. * true: Absolute Occurrence data is copied on variant item creation.
